{"tid":772654,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【兔迷】兔兔會不會發夢? 🐰","createTime":"2018-08-09T02:46:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T10:27:54.000Z","uid":197098,"like":31,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"90a3c77a8fa07b6311d0fba6e29f0172f739afaa","tid":772654,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T02:46:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">當然會，以下videos 可看到：<br />\n<br />\n發夢同主人玩：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s-7b9X5x_Ro\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Ds-7b9X5x_Ro&d=6NkRw8bGVUbXH5PeR8OX0%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=b8e771f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s-7b9X5x_Ro</a><br />\n<br />\n發夢喝水：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/koTWmdwLlp8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkoTWmdwLlp8&d=6NkRw8bGVUbXH5PeR8OX0%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=0d41c2f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/koTWmdwLlp8</a><br />\n<br />\n發夢吃香蕉：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-nDqlfAW-xE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-nDqlfAW-xE&d=6NkRw8bGVUbXH5PeR8OX0%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=d1597a6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-nDqlfAW-xE</a></span>"},{"pid":"60d42e56084918e59c42210327c5611771c8b6ae","tid":772654,"uid":197098,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T02:48:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">實在有太多主人遺棄兔子，主要原因是不理解兔子,覺得牠們悶不親近人。兔子是聰明、群體性動物。如果想養，可在兔友協會領養，這裏有太多兔子需要一個家。詳情可去 <a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2F%3Fpage_id%3D114&d=6NkRw8bGVUbXH5PeR8OX0%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=8fd63ff2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114</a> </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">撫摸兔仔很重要! 增加自尊心!🐰🐰</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">在大自然內，兔仔有牠們的等級制度。一個高級(dominant)的兔仔會groom (舔和梳理) 一個次級(inferior)的兔仔。但高級的亦會要求次級的兔仔groom 牠，這是一定要服從的。當兔仔低頭向前躺在地上，牠就是想你groom (撫摸和親吻) 牠，這樣可以增加牠的自尊心、令牠舒適、快樂、心理健康。當牠們受驚時，也需要groom牠們，令牠們冷靜下來和知道是沒事的。<br />\n<br />\n兔仔是被捕獵的動物(prey animal)，在大自然內是每個捕獵者(predatory animal)的目標，沒有自然本能去攻擊他人，但牠們勝於速度, 跑得快。牠們是脆弱的動物，很容易受驚的。兔子喜歡吸引人注意，有時我們看電視的時候，兔子會躺在電視機前面，幸好牠們不知道我們其實不在看牠們。因此，經常陪牠們玩是重要的，兔子是群體性動物，如果主人沒有空，最好領養多一隻兔子陪伴牠。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>以下video是一個等級制度的例子, 可以在0:59 看到：</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Nyv4VhuZv_s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNyv4VhuZv_s&d=6NkRw8bGVUbXH5PeR8OX0%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=299077fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Nyv4VhuZv_s</a> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果你在兔兔面前打開手掌，對於牠來說是要求牠groom 你。如果主人和兔兔的關係好，牠會groom主人。如果牠對主人感到憤怒，對於牠來說，在牠面前打開手掌是不尊重牠，牠可能會用屁股對着你(代表生悶氣) 或嚴重的話，撲過來咬你。兔子憤怒的時候，耳朵會放在後面，耳口向側，姿勢站起來很硬對着你。(這個耳朵擺放姿勢同驚慌一樣，但驚慌時坐姿會蹲下。大家可以看我寫兔子驚慌的post) 以下video 是主人要求兔兔groom 主人的例子：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6DKeKyzZ67Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6DKeKyzZ67Y&d=6NkRw8bGVUbXH5PeR8OX0%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=6b72c7d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6DKeKyzZ67Y</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><em><ins>有趣視頻:</ins></em></strong></span> <span style=\"font-size: large;\">兩隻兔子正在決定等級制度，但遇到困難。兔子A groom 兔子B, 但groom 了很久和等了很久還未得到回報(兔子B groom A作為回報)，所以發脾氣在2:08咬兔子B。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/af7_mGuD5Qg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Faf7_mGuD5Qg&d=6NkRw8bGVUbXH5PeR8OX0%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=00d8fd4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/af7_mGuD5Qg</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">為什麼兔仔咬籠子？🐰🐰😊</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">兔子咬籠其實是想引主人注意，覺得悶，告訴主人牠想出來玩和探索。兔子咬東西是自然的，牠們在大自然是用腳和牙齒來掘洞穴。由於牠們的牙齒不斷生長，咬東西可以幫牠們磨短。喜歡咬東西的兔子是聰明、親切、喜歡引人注意(或其他兔注意)。有時候主人正在整理東西，牠們過來其實想一起參與。除了提供無限Hay幫助牠們磨牙外，主人可以買一些草墊、草屋、cardboard給牠們咬。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><em><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">兔子親吻主人，這是代表你是一個好主人，以下2個videos 可看到：</span></strong></em></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Maovq8Vz1LM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMaovq8Vz1LM&d=6NkRw8bGVUbXH5PeR8OX0%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=bc840709\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Maovq8Vz1LM</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pyL0yEs-ka8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DpyL0yEs-ka8&d=6NkRw8bGVUbXH5PeR8OX0%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=e308f28e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pyL0yEs-ka8</a> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><em><span style=\"color: maroon;\">Advanced rabbit tricks! Amazing!: </span></em></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dLCEU3baplk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdLCEU3baplk&d=6NkRw8bGVUbXH5PeR8OX0%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=9799c703\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dLCEU3baplk</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兔子深入資訊：<a href=\"http://rabbit.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org&d=6NkRw8bGVUbXH5PeR8OX0%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=c04e4300\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbit.org</a> <br />\n關於兔子身體語言(害怕、開心、憂愁、憤怒): <a href=\"http://rabbitspeak.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbitspeak.com&d=6NkRw8bGVUbXH5PeR8OX0%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=181dfdb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbitspeak.com</a>"},{"pid":"d4863c262b7d0f42766a26d614f4dc854ac2862b","tid":772654,"uid":21305,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T02:52:55.000Z","msg":"得意， 但行過金魚街成日覺得好臭"},{"pid":"a439a29ee6b2b0da4e38bd29f5dfe5dc5ea28b90","tid":772654,"uid":17232,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T02:55:37.000Z","msg":"樓主有心 lm先"},{"pid":"ef6718e0051454a87c557e80b9b52f922ddc2def","tid":772654,"uid":98507,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T03:45:41.000Z","msg":"代養過幾日 唔知係咪新環境冇安全感<br />\n唔捉佢都唔出黎<br />\n不過放左佢出籠一日<br />\n同佢玩下波抱多兩抱就懶熟咁攤係我大脾un下un下咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最鍾意係由頭摸到身嗰時<br />\n佢好自然後傾對耳比你順住摸嗰下<br />\n仲要合埋眼 好撚治癒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"306990a925c5b5984d847b3cfe060a5996dc9465","tid":772654,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ef6718e0051454a87c557e80b9b52f922ddc2def","tid":772654,"uid":98507,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T03:45:41.000Z","msg":"代養過幾日 唔知係咪新環境冇安全感<br />\n唔捉佢都唔出黎<br />\n不過放左佢出籠一日<br />\n同佢玩下波抱多兩抱就懶熟咁攤係我大脾un下un下咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最鍾意係由頭摸到身嗰時<br />\n佢好自然後傾對耳比你順住摸嗰下<br />\n仲要合埋眼 好撚治癒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T03:48:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece18737133d9bc38ed1fe420ddb52d869cdc908","tid":772654,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:32:53.000Z","msg":"現在幾多歲？什麼品種？"},{"pid":"979a6cdd6c2d5996144fc57cbfec470156cf94ed","tid":772654,"uid":144,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:48:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/09/124751_0c7a2f7e76b5bc5265885e834d040970.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F09%2F124751_0c7a2f7e76b5bc5265885e834d040970.png&h=856fd135&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌你老母😒"},{"pid